title: Quiz: Which Forgettable President Are You?
description: Which of these forgettable presidents are you!

jt.title: John Tyler
jt.description: You are likely super unpopular, and often play second fiddle to others

mf.title: Millard Fillmore
mf.description: You are often a source of conflict despite not trying to be

jb.title: James Buchanan
jb.description: You are a literal doormat, all you do is stand there and get rolled over

mb.title: Martin Van Buren
mb.description: Your love of expensive things will be your downfall

wm.title: William McKinley
wm.description: A consummate politician, your beliefs are whatever people around you want them to be

wh.title: Warren G. Harding
wh.description: You’d rather do anything but work, but you are charismatic enough to keep failing up

questions.prompt: You are forced to sing in front of a large group of people, what do you sing?
B. The Soviet National Anthem
D. Paradise City - Guns N Roses
F. A rap song you only know half the words to so you do the microphone point thing
You’re invited to a costume party, which of these are you wearing?
B. The same costume as the popular kid because that’s just your luck
D. A super elaborate Joker costume
F. A ghost for the third year in a row
We here at The Snitch have nothing to do on Friday nights because we are lonely, what would you do?
B. Accidentally start a fight at the bar
D. Partyyyyy
F. Chat up influential people
You accidentally start a new trend, what is it?
B. Fencing with sticks
D. Collecting super expensive rocks
F. Something that you can do while being lazy
From legal fees to OSHA violations The Snitch has made many enemies, who would be your worst enemy?
B. Peace
D. The tax collector
F. Any sort of hard work
In order to fight these charges we need some good friends, which of these make the best friends?
B. The loud wisecracking kid
D. Diamonds duh
F. Your smoking buddy
